ious trends that folks have noticed, and my own research, here's what seems to be the case.<br>
<br>
Spells of the same level have the same trivial point, regardless of class. (Nullify Magic for enchanters seems to be the only anomaly mentioned.)<br>
<br>
I'll leave the trivial points of restoring faded pages to an enchanter.<br>
<br>
Some of these are estimates, but they should be pretty darned close. If anyone has any data that contradicts this, please share: morty@necrognomicon.com<br>
